{"tid":2043924,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人記得細個睇數碼暴龍 超比多獸出招比吸血魔獸截停？","createTime":"2020-05-30T17:50:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T19:12:19.000Z","uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f4253b34d3ab04ce9d50703476a36c051d34e05f","tid":2043924,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T17:50:18.000Z","msg":"即係天女獸打到吸血魔獸就收皮<br />\n大家用最後一招執雞<br />\n然後個個都出絕招 係遠攻<br />\n得超比多獸想用招濕鳩技撞鳩過去<br />\n但吸血魔獸用眼神截停咗佢<br />\n成個唔明點解呢幕咁on9<br />\n明明吸血魔獸都就死<br />\n點解仲要整呢段嚟晒時間<br />\n有無人記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29ccef88ad6ba9717d78051d386c05b4d9cd40a","tid":2043924,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T17:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea28cdb96b7fe439d2ce9de6792a8c8c2c21853","tid":2043924,"uid":141285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T17:54:38.000Z","msg":"超比多獸知自己羸唔到但都要都衝埋去"},{"pid":"32a6766eef4df72a0171650deefc7ad22430e292","tid":2043924,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T18:17:45.000Z","msg":"20年前既野你都記到依家有冇咁深刻<br />\n係咪哩20年黎晚晚都諗點解哩幕係咁"},{"pid":"fdbf8109391513cbbfca33b48b621fa66d3a825a","tid":2043924,"uid":70021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T18:21:15.000Z","msg":"邊有呢幕 剛剛去重睇都無"},{"pid":"2c646c03e7992e54b2c5d98b6fbd3f780484968a","tid":2043924,"uid":70021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T18:23:32.000Z","msg":"明明超比多鳩衝埋去係天女獸出來之前<br />\n全世界都唔夠吸血魔獸打<br />\n超比多鳩衝埋去畀吸血魔獸用技彈走<br />\n後尾天女獸先出黎收頭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad29e2a91e379c828fe0b3eaf83639d3b8a0646","tid":2043924,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fdbf810